        <item>
          <title>The Chiefs get more Mahomes magic and advance to 3rd straight Super Bowl, beating the Bills 32-29</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Patrick Mahomes threw for 245 yards and a touchdown, ran through the Buffalo defense for two more scores, and relied on his defense at key moments to help the Kansas City Chiefs beat the Bills 32-29 on Sunday night and reach the Super Bowl for the third consecutive season.]]></description>
